Detroit Lions player Reggie Bush on Tuesday compared the shooting death of unarmed teenager Michael Brown to Palestine on social media.

The running back posted on his Instagram account a photo of a man holding a sign with the message: 'The Palestinian People know what mean to be shot while unarmed because of your ethnicity. #Ferguson #Justice.'

The sign suggested that unarmed Palestinians were being shot by Israel.

